| **Expected Savings & Benefits**                                       | - Improves visibility of unresolved Cohesity backup failures. <br>- Reduces manual validation and reporting effort. <br>- Avoids duplicate incident creation. <br>- Provides consistent ServiceNow incident updates. <br>- Reduces detection gaps between scheduled cycles using email alerts and PowerShell ad-hoc validation. <br>- Converts backup failure visibility into a controlled operational tracking workflow.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
